channel.title: Testers Wanted!
channel.description:
[html]

The name of this testers-only version is: whonix-137adretemp.

Please test and leave feedback!

When Tor 0.2.4 comes out, this will probably become the next stable version of Whonix.

Download links:

* http://sourceforge.net/projects/whonixdevelopermetafiles/files/whonix-137adretemp/Whonix-Workstation-137adretemp.ova/download * http://sourceforge.net/projects/whonixdevelopermetafiles/files/whonix-137adretemp/Whonix-Workstation-137adretemp.ova.asc/download

OpenPGP signatures:

* http://sourceforge.net/projects/whonixdevelopermetafiles/files/whonix-137adretemp/Whonix-Gateway-137adretemp.ova/download * http://sourceforge.net/projects/whonixdevelopermetafiles/files/whonix-137adretemp/Whonix-Gateway-137adretemp.ova.asc/download

The changelog is way too long but feel free to look at http://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/featureblog/2013/07/testers-wanted-new-testers-only-version-whonix-97adretemp/ and the git log.

Cheers, adrelanos

[/html]
